name: MusmeCoin
description: What is CoinMusme? CoinMusme transforms complex Web3 concepts into accessible entertainment through anime-style idol characters ("coin waifus") representing different cryptocurrencies. Launched by TechCross, the platform combines traditional Japanese gacha gaming mechanics with blockchain technology, where characters compete in price prediction races and idol performances. Users can play NFT card battles and Price Prediction race of different cryptocurrencies to get project token $MSM as a reward.
